                        <h1 className="text-[2rem] font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tighter leading-tight mb-2">VocaQuest</h1>
                        <p className="text-slate-400 font-bold text-sm">Select your language / ?Ėņ¢┤ļź??ĀĒāØ?śņäĖ??/p>
